NK039(ti)010:0: de nas re ma ti la /
NK039(ti)010:1: bdud re lde mgo nyag gis /
NK039(ti)010:2: 'dul thabs kyi dbang gi sgo nas bstod pa /
NK039(ti)010:3: lha la dbang bsgyur lha mo dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)010:4: dbang phyug sras mo lha mo gzi ldan ma //
NK039(ti)010:5: sum cu rtsa gsum gnas kyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)010:6: lha mo re ma ti la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)010:7: bdud la dbang bsgyur bdud mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)010:8: re lde 'gong nyag bu mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)010:9: nag mo rtse dgu'i gnas kyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)010:10: bdud mo re ma ti la phyag klu la dbang
NK039(ti)010:11: bsgyur gtsug na rin chen bu mo yid 'ong ma
NK039(ti)010:12: // rol mtsho bdun gyi gnas kyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)010:13: klu mo re ma ti la gnod sbyin dbang bsgyur gang ba bzang po'i bu mo shang ka na //
NK039(ti)010:14: nags tshal d+r+wa ba can gyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)010:15: gnod sbyin re ma ti la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)010:16: zhes me lce 'bar ba'i rgyud kyi bstod pa khol phyung lags ////
NK039(ti)010:17: b+h+yo ma cig lha mo gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)010:18: sring gcig lha mo gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)010:19: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam gcig ma //
NK039(ti)010:20: nad dang rim gyi bdag mo chen mo khyod //
NK039(ti)010:21: thugs dam bskang phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)010:22: nyams chag sel phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)010:23: phrin las sgrub phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)010:24: bskang ngo bskal pas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:25: 'bod pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir /
NK039(ti)010:26: zhing chen g.yab mos thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:27: brten pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)010:28: mi dbang snying gis thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:29: 'bod pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)010:30: zhing chen g.yab mos thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:31: brten pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)010:32: mi dbang snying gis thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:33: rang bzhin gnas nas spyan 'dren phyir //
NK039(ti)010:34: mi rkang gling bus thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:35: dam tshig gnyan po bsre ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)010:36: bdud rtsi sman gyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:37: 'dod khams gtso mo yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)010:38: rma bya'i rgyal mtshan thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:39: ljags kyi dbang po tshim bya'i phyir //
NK039(ti)010:40: sha chen rus pas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:41: mgrin pa'i gsang nas sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)010:42: dmar chen rak+tasa thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:43: nyams chag ma lus gso ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)010:44: bya nag lug nag g.yag nag gis //
NK039(ti)010:45: dkar mo 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:46: ser mo 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:47: dmar mo 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:48: ljang mo 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:49: smug mo 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:50: mthing nag 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:51: ma yams rgyal mo'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:52: bod khams brtan ma'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:53: 'dzam gling skyong ma'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)010:54: ma khyod kyang dam la ma 'da' zhig /
NK039(ti)010:56: gal te dam la 'da' gyur na //
NK039(ti)010:57: srog gi snying po me 'bar bas //
NK039(ti)010:58: rang srog rang gis gcod par byed //
NK039(ti)010:59: de bas dam la ma 'da' bar //
NK039(ti)010:60: thugs dam gnyan po 'di bskang nas //
NK039(ti)010:61: nyams chag gyur na bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)010:62: sku gsung thugs kyis dngos grub stsol //
NK039(ti)010:63: phrin las drag shul mthu ma chung //
NK039(ti)010:64: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)010:65: yi ge brgya pas kha bskang bar bya'o //
